HEADWORD: Brownwort
<hw>Brown"wort`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A species of figwort or <gen>Scrophularia</gen> (<spn>Scrophularia
vernalis</spn>), and other species of the same genus, mostly perennials
with inconspicuous coarse flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

